snippet.title: Super Mario Kart R Beta Recreation Trailer (Project R)
snippet.description:
We welcome you all back to a time when Mario Kart 64 wasn't 64 at all! This rom hack of Mario Kart 64 aims to meticulously recreate the build all E3 1996 attendees we're greeted to but this time in playable form!

This trailer was featured in Kaze’s F3.

Project R Discord:https://discord.gg/m9JzzNVJZn
Twitter:https://twitter.com/ProjectR1996
Music by Paulygon: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qs2VtNq318k
